      "writtenOn": "2015-12-21T13:20:54Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027d recommend using |--name| instead of |-name| for options. The fact that the emulator only supports |-name| is a mistake and we should fix it (e.g. by making --name and -name equivalent).\n\nAlso -name or --name is normally reserved for options, why not make it a simple command instead? (i.e. just \u0027name\u0027).",
